{"tid":192481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母自由黨推薦廿蚊張做教育局長？","createTime":"2017-04-08T15:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T09:01:59.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d849b8bdda6d00d9055038fd73987fb8b98e1a0f","tid":192481,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T15:26:49.000Z","msg":"now新聞報道，自由黨黨魁鍾國斌出席該台節目《大鳴大放》時表示，自由黨會向候任行政長官林鄭月娥推薦合適的黨員加入政府班子，他認為自由黨主席張宇人適合出任教育局局長。鍾國斌又表示 ，林鄭月娥當選以來表現不錯，有落區接觸市民 ，亦願意邀請泛民各黨派會面，期望她上任後能重建立法會以至社會互信。<br />\n<br />\n《明報》引述張宇人被問到這事時說，「誤人子弟，何必呢？」<br />\n<br />\n鍾國斌又進一步向《明報》解釋，張宇人本身是中文大學校董，又是拔萃男書院資深校董，他的太太亦是資深教育界從業員，所以張宇人在大中小學方面都熟悉。"},{"pid":"7960a937d0f2daa6c9a3be1dfbc23c3610ac0db9","tid":192481,"uid":23120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T15:29:20.000Z","msg":"鍾玩膠佢姐,佢本身係撐JT"},{"pid":"12dee039e8bf01f78a61d8b4b09f7eeafed3cfcc","tid":192481,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T07:27:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鍾玩膠佢姐,佢本身係撐JT</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/x2lbnm3p\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fx2lbnm3p&h=16c57fc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n田大少語氣似有心玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dcde9e99e78d46ca02c62b4a8520846ee092c61","tid":192481,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:01:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鍾玩膠佢姐,佢本身係撐JT</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/x2lbnm3p\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fx2lbnm3p&h=16c57fc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n田大少語氣似有心玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明顯唔gur 佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94dc082279cd9c8db944a3b98177c7f777a2e199","tid":192481,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:19:27.000Z","msg":"成日係喜來登 雪茄吧見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時教學生食煙？<br />\n<br />\n利申，打過呢間酒店工"},{"pid":"cd5c63720490813f5aa728b3b47acd122cb5f2de","tid":192481,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T09:01:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鍾玩膠佢姐,佢本身係撐JT</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/x2lbnm3p\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fx2lbnm3p&h=16c57fc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n田大少語氣似有心玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明顯唔gur 佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大班有次爆料話將乳淫過橋抽板，佢有今日完全係田大少幫佢撘路，點知條撚屌依家唔企大少嗰邊仲入行會"}]}